Step1-Apache2 installation :	yum install httpd
Step2-Mysql installation :	yum install mysql-server
Step3-PHP installation :	yum install php
Step4-php-mysql:		yum install php-mysql
I got an error "Cake is NOT able to connect to the database". This error caused by php-mysql is missing. 
We must install php-mysql pack.
Ref link: http://www.krizna.com/centos/installing-apache2-mysql-server-php-centos-6-lamp/

